opinions.text:
Opinion
per Curiam,
The order dismissing the appellant’s petition for a writ of habeas corpus is affirmed on the opinion of Judge Toal for the court below, which fully and satisfaetorily answers tbe reasons advanced by the appellant in support of Ms petition.
Order affirmed.
opinions.author: per Curiam,

Ernest L. Green, Assistant District Attorney, and J. Harold Hughes, First Assistant District Attorney, and Raymond R. Start, District Attorney, for appellee.
